videos.headline: Utah LB burns former team with pick-6
videos.description: Zach Wilson throws an interception straight to Utah's Francis Bernard, the former BYU Cougar who returns it 58 yards for touchdown, giving Utah a 9-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wilson INT leads to Utah 58-yd TD) 2019/08/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU's Wilson sprints for big 26-yd gain
videos.description: Zach Wilson escapes pressure, shakes a defender and runs 26-yards to put BYU in the red zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU's Wilson sprints for big 26-yd gain) 2019/08/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dixon stretches out to extend Utah's lead
videos.description: Jaylen Dixon stretches out for a two-yard touchdown to increase Utah's lead to 16-6 over BYU in the 3rd quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dixon stretches out to extend Utah's lead) 2019/08/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson throws 2nd pick-6 of the night
videos.description: Zach Wilson's pass is bobbled and intercepted by Utah's Julian Blackmon who returns it 39 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Utah's defense forces 2 picks in win vs. BYU
videos.description: BYU quarterback Zach Wilson throws two interceptions as Utah finishes Week 1 with a 30-12 road victory.
